      - generic [ref=e455]:
        - heading "Upcoming Events" [level=2] [ref=e456]
        - paragraph [ref=e457]: With life enrichment activities to meet every interest, you can be as busy as you choose to be at Presbyterian Senior Living communities. Here are a few upcoming events designed to ensure the body, mind, and spirit thrive.
      - paragraph [ref=e460]:
